Uses of Package
app.model

Packages that use app.model
Package
Description
app
This package contains the main driver, Photos, and the model package which contains core classes and models for the Photo Management Application.
app.model
This package contains the model classes for the Photo Management Application.
view
This package contains the controllers for the FXML components of the Photo Management Application.
